public final byte[] getHash(java.lang.String hashAlgorithm)
                     throws java.security.NoSuchAlgorithmException
This method returns the hash of the encryptions of the vote (no random factors, nor verification values). It uses the method getCandideVotesHash of the MP3VoteFactory class

Parameters:
hashAlgorithm - hash algorithm
Returns:
the hash of the vote (only candidate vote and commit encryptions are considered)
Throws:
java.security.NoSuchAlgorithmException - if the hashAlgorithm is not supported
